definitions.definition: A book in which measurements from the ship's log are recorded, along with other salient details of the voyage.
A book in which events are recorded; a journal , especially of travel.
A record of the ownership , and licensing of a motor car .

main_definition: ( nautical ) A book in which measurements from the ship's log are recorded, along with other salient details of the voyage.
secondary_definitions: ( by extension ) A book in which events are recorded; a journal , especially of travel.
( UK ) A record of the ownership , and licensing of a motor car .
